flowchart TD
    Q{Agent 在每一步前<br/>必须能定位到下面六个动作之一}
    Q --> C[continue<br/>证据充足 + 授权清晰]
    Q --> D[deny<br/>请求超出权限范围]
    Q --> H[hold<br/>等待外部输入]
    Q --> E[escalate<br/>升级到更高权限节点]
    Q --> AU[audit_flag<br/>状态可疑,触发审计]
    Q --> CL[close<br/>满足全部 closure 条件<br/>带 closure receipt]

    style Q fill:#fff8e1,stroke:#1F4E79,stroke-width:2px
    style C fill:#d4edda,stroke:#2e7d32
    style CL fill:#d4edda,stroke:#2e7d32
    style D fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#c79100
    style H fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#c79100
    style E fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#c79100
    style AU fill:#fdeeee,stroke:#c0392b
